    {
      "id": "p002",
      "index": 2,
      "source": "The trend is real but plateauing. iPhone unit volumes have matured. Any demand increase reflects larger die sizes on newer nodes. By 2030, A-series falls below 30% of Apple’s total wafer demand, down from 92% in 2014.",
      "source_html": null,
      "element_type": "p",
      "inline_elements": [],
      "parent_block_id": "b0243",
      "parent_block_index": 243,
      "parent_block_type": "p",
      "parent_block_markdown": "The trend is real but plateauing. iPhone unit volumes have matured. Any demand increase reflects larger die sizes on newer nodes. By 2030, A-series falls below 30% of Apple’s total wafer demand, down from 92% in 2014.",
      "parent_block_plain_text": "The trend is real but plateauing. iPhone unit volumes have matured. Any demand increase reflects larger die sizes on newer nodes. By 2030, A-series falls below 30% of Apple’s total wafer demand, down from 92% in 2014.",
      "parent_source_html": null,
      "parent_inline_elements": [],
      "segment_start": 0,
      "segment_end": 217,
      "expected_tokens": [],
      "format_recovery_status": "not_applicable",
      "format_errors": [],
      "is_heading": false,
      "heading_level": null,
      "heading_chain": [],
      "is_metadata": false,
      "metadata_type": null,
      "translations": {
        "pro": {
          "text": "这一增长趋势确切无疑，但已触及天花板。iPhone 的出货量已步入成熟期。任何需求的增长均源于新制程节点上裸片尺寸的增大。到 2030 年，A系列在苹果总晶圆需求中的占比将从 2014 年的 92% 跌破 30%。",
          "model": "pro",
          "created_at": "2026-04-10T16:22:51.472178",
