    {
      "id": "p005",
      "index": 5,
      "source": "Even with that slowdown, M-series reaches 60% of A-series demand by 2030. The crossover is approaching. If M-series growth reaccelerates, perhaps through new categories like AI-centric Macs, the lines could cross before 2035.",
      "source_html": null,
      "element_type": "p",
      "inline_elements": [],
      "parent_block_id": "b0246",
